---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Grid from "../components/grid.astro";
import Deal from "../components/Deal.astro";
import Why from "../components/Why.astro";
import Button from "../components/Button.astro";
---

<Layout title="about page">
  <main>
    <!-- section-1 -->

    <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#252d4b] to-[#4b5eaa]">
      <div
        class="infra-banner sm:bg-right bg-left-bottom item-center flex xl:h-[430px] lg:min-h-[370px] sm:h-[300px] h-[330px] w-full relative"
      >
        <img
          src="../../public/assets/Mask_group.png"
          class="lg:w-auto sm:w-2/3 w-4/5 h-full object-fill absolute right-0 block"
        />
        <div class="container-1 text-white space-y-5">
          <h1 class="md:text-3xl sm:text-2xl text-xl md:w-1/2">
            We are Your Trusted Partner For Infrastructure & Lubricant Product
            Needs.
          </h1>
          <p class="md:w-1/2 ptag">
            Mignesh Global is the leading provider of range of high-quality
            products such as Bitumen, Bitumen Emulsion, Base Oil, Furnace Oil,
            etc to fulfill your Infrastructure or lubricant product needs.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- section-2 -->
    <section class="mt-[100px]">
      <div
        class="container-1
         flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-10"
      >
        <div class="space-y-5">
          <div>
            <p class="orange">About Us</p>
            <h2 class="purple uppercase">Mignesh Global Ltd</h2>
          </div>
          <div
            class="w-full lg:max-w-[575px] xl:max-w-[582px] 2xl:max-w-[575px] space-y-4 ptag"
          >
            <p>
              Mignesh Global paved their way with Mignesh Trading in 2016 and is
              the leading provider of an extensive range of products such as
              Bitumen, Bitumen Emulsion, Base Oil, and Furnace Oil tailored to
              meet the needs of both Infrastructure and Manufacturing companies.
            </p>

            <p>
              Our unwavering dedication to providing products of the highest
              quality, all conveniently available in one place, has been the
              cornerstone of our success over the past seven years.
            </p>
            <p>
              To deliver the best in class customer satisfaction and optimum
              quality products, Mignesh Global remains at the forefront of
              industry trends and aligned with customer preferences, while
              ensuring continued growth and prominence in the market.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <img src="../../public/assets/Images.svg" alt="" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- section-3 -->
    <section
      class="mt-[100px] bg-[#E4E7EC] grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 justify-items-center content-center"
    >
      <div
        class="bg-[url(../../public/assets/Mask_group1.png)] p-5 sm:py-28 md:py-32 lg:p-0 bg-no-repeat bg-cover bg-right w-screen md:w-full"
      >
        <div
          class="max-sm:px-[25px] max-sm:text-center md:pr-20 lg:pr-0 md:text-left sm:max-w-[555px] md:max-w-[672px] max-lg:m-auto lg:ml-auto lg:mr-[45px] lg:max-w-[420px] xl:max-w-[500px] xl:mr-[60px] 2xl:max-w-[575px] lg:pt-[100px]"
        >
          <h6 class="orange">Our Story</h6>
          <h2 class="purple">
            The Journey of Blending Tech for Infrastructure & Manufacturing
            Industry!
          </h2>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="py-10 m-auto lg:pt-[100px] lg:pb-[62px] max-sm:px-[25px] sm:max-w-[555px] md:max-w-[672px] space-y-4 ptag lg:max-w-[320px] lg:ml-[110px] xl:max-w-[457px] 2xl:max-w-[520px]"
      >
        <p>
          In this tech-savvy environment, where technology has been evolving at
          a breakneck pace - shaping the face of varied industries - our
          founders wondered why not the Infrastructure & production industry.
        </p>
        <p>
          That's when a team of experts in the infrastructure and manufacturing
          industry came together to create something extraordinary. With a
          burning passion and a shared vision, they set out to develop a
          platform that would transform the industry.
        </p>
        <p>
          And so, Mignesh Global Ltd was born in 2016. We developed a
          tech-driven ERP platform that aims to simplify the entire process of
          getting high-quality products for infrastructure and production
          companies in one place.
        </p>
        <p>
          We have a range of products such as Bitumen, Bitumen Emulsion, Base
          Oil, and Furnace Oil on this platform, which everyone can avail of
          through an easy-to-use interface and quick process.
        </p>
        <p>
          But their success wasn't just about creating a platform - it was about
          creating a long-lasting relationship with their customers.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- section-4 -->
    <section class="mt-[100px]">
      <div
        class="space-y-5 gap-5 container-1 flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-between"
      >
        <div class="w-full purple uppercase">
          <h2>Our Vision, Mission</h2>
          <div class="flex lg:flex flex-wrap justify-between">
            <h2>& Core Values!</h2>
            <img
              class="sm:pt-2 max-lg:w-full"
              src="../../public/assets/Vector1.svg"
              alt=""
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-5 w-full">
          <Grid
            path="../../public/assets/mission.svg"
            para="At Mignesh Global Ltd, we're on a mission to revolutionize the infrastructure and manufacturing industry by offering the platform to avail the best products in just a few easy steps. We believe that giving businesses all products at one location while making the process efficient, reliable, and cost-effective."
            head="Mission"
          />
          <Grid
            path="../../public/assets/our_approach.svg"
            para="Our vision is to create an easy-to-use platform driven by innovative tech that simplifies the entire process of sourcing products for the infrastructure and manufacturing industry. Our commitment to helping businesses achieve their goals is at the heart of everything we do."
            head="Vision"
          />
          <Grid
            path="../../public/assets/Vector.svg"
            para="At Mignesh Global Ltd, we are committed to upholding our integrity, transparency, and customer-centricity values. We strive to create long-lasting relationships with our customers by providing them with the best possible solutions."
            head="Our Values"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- section-5 -->
    <section
      class="text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-[#252d4b] to-[#4b5eaa] mt-[100px]"
    >
      <div
        class="gap-10 lg:gap-[83px] py-10 lg:p-0 lg:pb-40 container-1 flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-center items-center"
      >
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div
            style="background: radial-gradient(50% 50% at 50% 50%, #FFF 31.25%, #F8DBC6 100%);"
          >
            <img
              class="max-w-[266.05px] pt-[90px] ps-[47px]"
              src="../../public/assets/Untitled-6 1.png"
              alt=""
            />
          </div>

          <div class="relative">
            <!-- Image -->
            <div class="absolute">
              <img src="../../public/assets/Polygon 5.svg" alt="" />
            </div>

            <!-- Text -->
            <div class="relative z-10">
              <h2>Arjun N. Pachani</h2>
              <h2>(Founder, Mignesh Global Pvt. Ltd)</h2>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="w-full lg:w-[550px] space-y-5">
          <div>
            <p class="orange">Meet</p>
            <div class="founder uppercase">
              <h2>our Founder!</h2>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4 ptag">
            <p>
              Arjun N. Pachani has been working in this industry for around 12
              years, and he is a civil engineer operating as a Promoting
              Director at Mignesh Group of Industries. Our Founder has been
              working to accelerate this industry for over a decade as an
              enthusiastic entrepreneur to change the face of Infrastructure in
              India by integrating technology efficiently.
            </p>

            <p>
              He always had a vision of simplifying these industries by blending
              them with technology. To make this possible, he founded this
              company back in 2016 while confronting the challenges in the
              infrastructure and production industry of getting the best
              products at one centralized location, affordable rates, and
              managed logistics.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- section-6 -->
    <section class="mt-[100px]">
      <div class="space-y-5 container-1">
        <div>
          <p class="orange">We deal in</p>
          <div class="purple uppercase">
            <h2>the following Products!</h2>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 justify-center items-center"
        >
          <Deal
            text1="Bitumen & "
            text2="Bitumen Products"
            path="../../public/assets/Group 110.png"
          />
          <Deal
            text1="Lubricant "
            text2="Raw Material"
            path="../../public/assets/Group 111.png"
          />
          <Deal
            text1="Building & Construction "
            text2="Raw Material"
            path="../../public/assets/Group 112.png"
          />
          <Deal
            text1="Petroleum"
            text2="Products"
            path="../../public/assets/Group 113.png"
          />
          <Deal
            text1="Polymer"
            text2="Products"
            path="../../public/assets/Group 114.png"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- section-7 -->

    <section class="bg-[#F9F9FB] mt-[100px]">
      <div class="py-[100px] space-y-5 container-1">
        <div>
          <p class="orange">Why</p>
          <div class="purple uppercase">
            <h2>Choose Us?</h2>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mx-auto justify-items-center content-center"
        >
          <Why
            path="../../public/assets/icon_High-Quality-Products.svg"
            para1="Products designed to meet the highest industry standards"
            para2="Wide range of products to choose from"
            para3="Products  tailored to meet specific project needs"
            head="High-Quality Products"
          />

          <Why
            path="../../public/assets/icon_Pocket-Friendly-Rates.svg"
            para1="Competitive pricing for all our products"
            para2="Savings without compromising on quality"
            para3="Transparent pricing with no hidden costs"
            head="Pocket-Friendly Rates"
          />

          <Why
            path="../../public/assets/icon_Seamless-Buying-Process.svg"
            para1="Easy-to-use interface for effortless navigation"
            para2="Simple and intuitive purchase process"
            para3="Efficient order management system for quick processing"
            head="Seamless Buying Process"
          />

          <Why
            path="../../public/assets/icon.svg"
            para1="Fast & Seamless delivery times for all products."
            para2="Our own Logistics company(Migesh Logistics) for prompt delivery."
            para3="Timely updates on the delivery status."
            head="Managed Logistics"
          />
          <Why
            path="../../public/assets/icon (1).svg"
            para1="Real-time tracking of purchased products."
            para2="Wide range of products to choose from"
            para3="Efficient after-sales support."
            head="End-to-End Tracking"
          />

          <Why
            path="../../public/assets/icon (2).svg"
            para1="Advanced technology for streamlining the entire process"
            para2="Disruptive solutions for enhancing efficiency"
            para3="Access to the latest technology in the industry"
            head="Tech-Driven ERP Platform"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- section-8 -->
    <section class="bg-[#E4E7EC]">
      <div class="py-14 container-1">
        <div
          class="flex flex-col-reverse md:flex-row max-md:text-center justify-between items-center gap-10"
        >
          <div class="space-y-5">
            <div class="purple">
              <h2>Source the high-quality products</h2>
              <h2>from the best ones!</h2>
            </div>

            <Button data="CONTACT NOW!" />
          </div>
          <div>
            <img src="../../public/assets/drum 1.png" alt="" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <style>
    .founder {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 24px;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .orange {
      color: #ea8135;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-style: normal;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 24px; /* 120% */
      letter-spacing: 0.2px;
    }
    .purple {
      color: #48389c;
      font-size: 32px;
      font-style: normal;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 40px;
      letter-spacing: 0.32px;
    }
    .ptag {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 24px;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
      text-align: left;
    }
    @media screen and (max-width: 425px) {
      .infra-banner {
        background-image: url(../../public/assets/Mask_group_small.png);
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        background-size: contain;
        height: 653px;
      }
      .infra-banner img {
        display: none;
      }
      .banner-text p {
        width: 100%;
        min-height: 800px;
        padding-top: 200px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
